snippet.title: Deterrence Gameplay Teaser Trailer October 2023
snippet.description:
Wishlist Now!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1972960/Deterrence/

Artificial intelligence has plotted a path to a sustainable future, but humans aren't included. Defend humanity against the A.I. in this instant action tower defense, real-time strategy hybrid.

If you'd like to know more, don't forget to follow and subscribe!

Official: https://deterrence.piscesstudios.com/

Trailer Music By: Oscar Leites https://www.youtube.com/c/OscarLeites
